
Useage:
1) Generate G4 simulation data -> Digitization using Calibration Data(auto.) -> Perform Reconstruction -> Analyze the rec results

2) Real detector data -> Perform reconstruction w/wo calibration(select.) -> Analyze the rec results



Info:
0-Simulation, G4 based simulation package, ".sroot" stands for simulation root file
1-Reconstruction, recon with two different methode, ".rec" stands for rec root file
2-Calibration, calibration package, readin real data and generate ".cal" for cal root file
3-Analysis, ...
4-EventDisplay, ...
CommonLib, ...


